{"tid":2338960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"的士司機毆清路障行家獲減刑3個月 官接納上訴人不知對方有舊患","createTime":"2020-12-24T10:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T11:09:21.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6002f887d331937deaaa557018f993dd77554303","tid":2338960,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"去年11月大三罷期間，有示威者在屯門鄉事會一帶堵路。中年的士司機駛經現場時，看見有同行清理路障，出言阻止不果，揮拳打向同行頭部，對方以手擋格，導致手腕舊患骨折。<span class=\"red\">涉案司機被裁定傷人罪成，判囚一年，早前向高等法院提出上訴，獲減刑至9個月</span>。法官黃崇厚今頒佈書面理由解釋，認為上訴人犯案時不知道事主有舊患，也非存心針對舊患施襲，評估上訴人出拳力度時也要避免過份推斷，故認為刑期有下調空間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/NY2BXGI7KJFRTDJV4GCHLS2YLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FNY2BXGI7KJFRTDJV4GCHLS2YLQ%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=15c8b09c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FNY2BXGI7KJFRTDJV4GCHLS2YLQ%2F&h=53a44ec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/NY2BXGI7KJFRTDJV4GCHLS2YLQ/</a>"},{"pid":"b3e3c3ccb28a21f3b4488a1af781240bb20e15b3","tid":2338960,"uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"原審署理主任裁判官張潔宜判上訴人監禁一年，並拒絕讓他保釋等候上訴。上訴人上周就定罪及刑期提出上訴，黃官駁回定罪上訴，但裁定刑期上訴得直，減刑3個月。"},{"pid":"1122d4d39ee5b6de4ec5ade76b0bdfd211e1f58e","tid":2338960,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d885f76f379c7ca412d6b8c34871a3187389c0","tid":2338960,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b87b34795a3cd9833a83b42501a0b